data.title: Long Haul Trucking, Namibia
data.meta_description: Canaan Group offers a long haul trucking and transport service to a wide range of clients in Namibia and in the SADC region.
data.text:
LONG HAUL TRUCKING

We currently service a wide range of clients domestically and in the SADC region. We mostly transport dry goods on flat- deck super links and also render services for abnormal loads. Our trucks are well maintained and are equipped with 24/7 tracking devices to give our clients peace of mind.

We have been contracted by some leading companies such as Rennies Consolidated, Whale Rock Cement, Ohorongo Cement and Corridor Logistic, to name just a few.
